title: As flood drowns drought-hit Bihar, it's a warning for Nitish Kumar
description: The Congress lost power in Bihar after worst of all floods in 1987. Lalu Prasad's RJD was voted out after 2004 flood. Warning for Nitish Kumar is that people compare the current flood in Patna with that of 1975.
content:
